<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Blog</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>


  <div id="top">
		<div id="topCenter">
			<div class="title">
  	 		<h1><a href="/">Sarah Riggs</a></h1>
				<p>Information Scientist</p>
			</div>
			<div class="icons">
				<p>test | test | test</p>
			</div>
				<p class="right"><%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path if admin_signed_in? %></p>

 		 </div>
	<div>


  <div id="middle">
		<div id="middleCenter">
			<% flash.each do |key, msg| %>
 			 <%= content_tag :div, msg, :id => key %>
			<% end %>
	   <%= yield %>
 	 	</div>
	<div>

  <div id="bottom">
		<div id="bottomCenter">

 		  <div id="bottomLeft">
				<p>Sarah Riggs, is an Information Scientists with a passion for making the user happy.</p>
				<p>She's not afraid to get her hands dirty, and not just because she used to be an Archaeologist. She loves jumping into to new projects especially if it involves playing with code and learning something off the wall.</p>
				<p>Sarah can often be found doodling, writing, and spending time outside.</p>
				<p>This is another paragraph</p>
				<p>This is another still</p>
			</div>

			<div id="bottomMiddle">
				<% @recent_posts.each do |post| %>
				<p><%= raw RedCloth.new(post.body.truncate(200)).to_html %><%= link_to ' Read More', post %></p>
				<% end %>
			</div>

			<div id="bottomRight">
				<p>@Diceratops</p>
				<p><a href="http://www.twitter.com/!/diceratops">Twitter</a></p>
				<p><a href="">LinkedIn</a></p>
				<p><a href="http://www.github.com/diceratops">GitHub</a></p>
				<p><a href="">Good Reads</a></p>
				<p><a href="">Rdio</a></p>
			</div>

	  </div>
	</div>

</body>
</html>
